1
00:01:03,640 --> 00:01:05,910
[Elegy of ZhaoLi]

2
00:01:06,180 --> 00:01:09,900
[Episode 16]

3
00:01:21,430 --> 00:01:21,950
Li.

4
00:01:22,039 --> 00:01:22,560
Li!

5
00:01:22,640 --> 00:01:23,280
Li!

6
00:01:23,789 --> 00:01:24,350
Li!

7
00:01:24,430 --> 00:01:25,039
Li.

8
00:01:25,430 --> 00:01:26,150
Li.

9
00:01:27,870 --> 00:01:29,230
You're finally awake.

10
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:31,789
How are you feeling?

11
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:34,070
I'm fine.

12
00:01:35,950 --> 00:01:37,759
It's all over now.

13
00:01:39,840 --> 00:01:41,479
Everything is over.

14
00:01:49,310 --> 00:01:50,200
What's wrong?

15
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:52,710
I have something for you.

16
00:01:55,789 --> 00:01:56,920
This letter

17
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:59,200
was hidden inside my mother's portrait.

18
00:01:59,759 --> 00:02:01,790
It was written by your father.

19
00:02:02,580 --> 00:02:03,830
Take a look.

20
00:02:04,590 --> 00:02:06,840
I'll... leave you alone for now.

21
00:02:23,430 --> 00:02:26,910
During a private inspection tour
in the past,

22
00:02:27,590 --> 00:02:29,800
I was fortunate to meet a woman

23
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:31,310
named Liu Yeqing.

24
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:34,910
She was both talented and virtuous,

25
00:02:34,910 --> 00:02:37,640
with a straightforward
and free-spirited personality,

26
00:02:37,640 --> 00:02:38,690
which made me

27
00:02:39,079 --> 00:02:40,710
yearn for her.

28
00:02:42,750 --> 00:02:43,880
However...

29
00:02:51,230 --> 00:02:52,070
Xingzhi.

30
00:02:52,280 --> 00:02:53,030
Yeqing.

31
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,470
Look at this flower you gave me.

32
00:03:00,470 --> 00:03:02,000
Why... Why has it wilted?

33
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:05,340
Did you water it improperly again?

34
00:03:05,470 --> 00:03:06,870
The roots are all soaked.

35
00:03:09,910 --> 00:03:11,800
Well, I'm so forgetful.

36
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:16,100
Greetings, Your Majesty.

37
00:03:16,100 --> 00:03:16,840
By the way,

38
00:03:17,910 --> 00:03:19,240
this is my husband,

39
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:22,100
Jiang Chengzhou, newly ranked scholar.

40
00:03:22,590 --> 00:03:23,910
Yes, that's me.

41
00:03:28,030 --> 00:03:28,910
These days,

42
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:31,630
I suddenly sensed a storm brewing.

43
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:34,630
So I'm specially
leaving this secret letter

44
00:03:34,630 --> 00:03:36,160
to seek a chance of survival

45
00:03:37,030 --> 00:03:39,190
for my son, Jiuzhao.

46
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:41,079
Your Majesty,

47
00:03:41,079 --> 00:03:42,560
people from General's Mansion
were in a hurry,

48
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:43,910
sending a letter
to the empress dowager's palace.

49
00:03:43,910 --> 00:03:46,240
I secretly swapped it and brought it here.

50
00:03:58,870 --> 00:03:59,750
Darn it!

51
00:03:59,910 --> 00:04:00,910
How dare they...

52
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,120
Order some guards

53
00:04:07,800 --> 00:04:09,730
to surround the Empress's palace.

54
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,690
Without my permission,

55
00:04:11,750 --> 00:04:14,520
no one is to leave the palace!

56
00:04:14,750 --> 00:04:15,360
Yes.

57
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:27,870
Xingzhi.

58
00:04:28,950 --> 00:04:29,830
Xingzhi,

59
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:32,159
why did you ask me here
with a secret letter at this hour?

60
00:04:32,159 --> 00:04:33,360
No time to explain.

61
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:34,360
Take these

62
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:35,830
and leave quickly with Jiuzhao!

63
00:04:35,830 --> 00:04:37,480
The imperial palace is in chaos now.

64
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:40,140
The Empress...
The Xuan clan will likely rebel.

65
00:04:40,430 --> 00:04:42,030
If anything happens to me...

66
00:04:44,750 --> 00:04:46,720
you must protect Jiuzhao.

67
00:04:47,190 --> 00:04:48,110
Yeqing,

68
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:50,000
you are my only true friend.

69
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:52,270
I can only entrust this to you.

70
00:04:52,430 --> 00:04:53,270
In the future,

71
00:04:53,270 --> 00:04:55,240
I hope you can help him.

72
00:04:56,390 --> 00:04:57,190
Okay.

73
00:04:58,830 --> 00:04:59,560
Go.

74
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:40,480
Are you okay?

75
00:05:52,800 --> 00:05:54,190
Actually, I knew

76
00:05:54,750 --> 00:05:56,000
about this long ago.

77
00:05:56,390 --> 00:06:00,320
The empress dowager has never shown
any motherly affection toward me.

78
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:02,360
She favors Nianzhao.

79
00:06:03,190 --> 00:06:04,270
I don't blame her.

80
00:06:05,510 --> 00:06:06,510
She hates me.

81
00:06:07,830 --> 00:06:09,800
I tried to pretend to ignore it.

82
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:11,420
But even if it's just maintaining

83
00:06:11,420 --> 00:06:13,830
a superficial mother-son relationship
with her,

84
00:06:13,830 --> 00:06:15,800
she wouldn't give me that chance.

85
00:06:20,270 --> 00:06:21,830
I even thought

86
00:06:22,390 --> 00:06:24,270
that if I died,

87
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:29,220
perhaps this family
would become somewhat different.

88
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:31,630
Everyone,

89
00:06:32,120 --> 00:06:32,600
[12 years ago]

90
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:34,380
the rebels who killed the emperor
have been executed

91
00:06:34,380 --> 00:06:36,510
along with their 9 clans
according to the law.

92
00:06:36,510 --> 00:06:37,630
However,

93
00:06:38,310 --> 00:06:40,950
a nation can't be without a ruler
for a single day.

94
00:06:40,950 --> 00:06:43,070
Since the Crown Prince's whereabouts
are unknown,

95
00:06:43,070 --> 00:06:46,310
-the 10th Prince, Xie Nianzhao...
-Wait!

96
00:06:50,890 --> 00:06:52,310
Liu Yeqing.

97
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:13,210
It's one thing
that you were reckless in the past,

98
00:07:13,510 --> 00:07:15,070
but this imperial assembly hall

99
00:07:15,070 --> 00:07:17,160
is no place for your insolence!

100
00:07:21,070 --> 00:07:22,310
-The Crown Prince?
-The Crown Prince?

101
00:07:22,310 --> 00:07:23,120
Yes.

102
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,240
The Crown Prince has returned.

103
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:25,900
It really is the Crown Prince.

104
00:07:30,390 --> 00:07:32,450
Since the Crown Prince has returned,

105
00:07:32,830 --> 00:07:35,680
there's nothing more to discuss.

106
00:07:36,070 --> 00:07:37,560
If you still have doubts,

107
00:07:37,630 --> 00:07:40,630
the late emperor gave the imperial seal
to the Crown Prince before his death.

108
00:07:40,630 --> 00:07:42,720
Everyone, you can bear witness.

109
00:07:53,390 --> 00:07:54,360
The imperial seal?

110
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:56,159
Is this really the imperial seal?

111
00:07:56,159 --> 00:07:59,400
Aunt Liu, why... why is this so heavy?

112
00:07:59,630 --> 00:08:01,870
Jiu, hold it carefully.

113
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:03,900
This is what your father gave you.

114
00:08:03,950 --> 00:08:06,920
This... This is indeed the imperial seal.

115
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:11,240
-Your Majesty, welcome back!
-Your Majesty, welcome back!

116
00:08:11,310 --> 00:08:16,430
-Long live the emperor!
-Long live the emperor!

117
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:29,280
The late emperor
entrusted the Crown Prince to me,

118
00:08:29,430 --> 00:08:32,360
so he naturally had his own plans.

119
00:08:33,150 --> 00:08:36,850
Your Majesty, for the sake
of the mother-son bond between you,

120
00:08:37,030 --> 00:08:39,360
please don't make another grave mistake.

121
00:08:46,030 --> 00:08:51,510
Long live the emperor!

122
00:09:05,550 --> 00:09:06,910
Thinking about it now,

123
00:09:08,150 --> 00:09:10,280
those executed in the palace back then

124
00:09:10,750 --> 00:09:12,320
were just scapegoats.

125
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:14,200
Father

126
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:17,440
was truly killed by his own wife.

127
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:19,670
Your own mother

128
00:09:20,030 --> 00:09:22,320
treats you like an enemy.

129
00:09:22,870 --> 00:09:25,790
As her child, you must be heartbroken.

130
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:36,790
My father is the same.

131
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:38,750
Ever since I was born,

132
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:40,840
he has disliked me.

133
00:09:41,910 --> 00:09:43,120
Now I understand.

134
00:09:43,630 --> 00:09:45,150
Every time he sees me,

135
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:46,670
he sees

136
00:09:47,550 --> 00:09:49,510
the shadow of my mother.

137
00:09:49,910 --> 00:09:51,270
It reminds him

138
00:09:51,960 --> 00:09:53,890
of how filthy and despicable he is.

139
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:57,000
Li,

140
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:59,440
you're not anyone's shadow.

141
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:00,790
You are wonderful.

142
00:10:01,630 --> 00:10:03,960
In my heart, you are uniquely good.

143
00:10:05,030 --> 00:10:07,200
You walked into my life.

144
00:10:07,270 --> 00:10:09,360
You are like the lamp in my life.

145
00:10:09,910 --> 00:10:11,440
Only then did I realize

146
00:10:11,670 --> 00:10:15,000
that there is still someone in this world
who cares about me.

147
00:10:15,120 --> 00:10:16,270
From now on,

148
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:19,600
I will protect you.

149
00:10:25,510 --> 00:10:27,840
But my world is too dangerous.

150
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:30,270
And you shouldn't be dragged

151
00:10:30,270 --> 00:10:31,730
into these dangers again.

152
00:10:37,360 --> 00:10:38,150
Zhao,

153
00:10:39,030 --> 00:10:41,840
in the past, my heart was like duckweed,

154
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:44,240
adrift and without support.

155
00:10:44,550 --> 00:10:45,550
But now,

156
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:49,080
we care about each other.

157
00:10:49,870 --> 00:10:51,550
So we'll spend the rest

158
00:10:51,550 --> 00:10:52,320
of our lives

159
00:10:52,750 --> 00:10:53,750
together.

160
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:57,720
Tomorrow, I will return
to the palace with you.

161
00:10:58,200 --> 00:11:00,790
No matter how difficult it will be
in the future,

162
00:11:00,790 --> 00:11:02,390
as long as you don't leave me,

163
00:11:02,480 --> 00:11:03,880
I will never abandon you.

164
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:30,910
♪ One last thread of longing ♪

165
00:11:31,450 --> 00:11:35,220
♪ Forgetting what regret feels like ♪

166
00:11:35,880 --> 00:11:39,840
♪ Letting time lie to us ♪

167
00:11:40,680 --> 00:11:44,000
♪ Turning over in the hands of fate ♪

168
00:11:44,710 --> 00:11:48,610
♪ The past that lives in my heart ♪

169
00:11:49,370 --> 00:11:53,420
♪ Is your quiet unease ♪

170
00:11:53,930 --> 00:11:55,860
♪ If life's answer ♪

171
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:57,960
♪ Is incomplete ♪

172
00:11:58,490 --> 00:12:01,590
♪ Then let me walk what's left with you ♪

173
00:12:02,060 --> 00:12:04,180
♪ Sandstorms filled the desert sky ♪

174
00:12:04,490 --> 00:12:07,130
♪ Yet they never buried this ♪

175
00:12:07,470 --> 00:12:10,820
♪ You promised everything,
without hesitation ♪

176
00:12:11,310 --> 00:12:12,900
♪ All for a single stroke of longing ♪

177
00:12:13,300 --> 00:12:15,460
♪ Even the brightest moments
fade like foam ♪

178
00:12:15,750 --> 00:12:19,820
♪ Wandering with me
to the edge of the world ♪

179
00:12:20,310 --> 00:12:22,500
♪ You held the fire
you lit with your heart ♪

180
00:12:22,840 --> 00:12:25,000
♪ And gave it to me without fear ♪

181
00:12:25,410 --> 00:12:26,470
♪ Even in the dead of night ♪

182
00:12:26,710 --> 00:12:29,760
♪ That flash of light ♪

183
00:12:30,160 --> 00:12:34,160
♪ Was the most beautiful moment of all ♪

184
00:12:34,780 --> 00:12:38,820
♪ You were the one who protected me ♪

185
00:12:39,610 --> 00:12:46,940
♪ You were the one who protected me ♪
